th? </div><div class="t m18f x1 h1e y8e5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m426 xca h1e y8e5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What has obedience to God&apos;s law by faith in Christ done for </div><div class="t md0 xca h1e y8e6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">you personally? What and where would you be today if you </div><div class="t m3fc xca h1e y8e7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">had not accepted the will of God as stated in His law? </div><div class="t m361 x34 h2a y8e8 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: </div><div class="t m19c x43 h1e y8e8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s law, commandments, and statutes are not bur-</div><div class="t m7a x34 h1e y8e9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">densome. The secret is to have them in the heart, which will be a </div><div class="t m67 x34 h1e y8ea ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">delight and make it a pleasure to obey them. </div><div class="t m6fd x21 h60 y387 ff5 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Don&apos;t ask that dollar where it went; </div><div class="t m516 x76 h60 y8eb ff5 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Tell it where to go! </div><div class="t m6fe xe h2a y8ec ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">— H. </div><div class="t m6ff x5 h1e y8ed ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">D. Singleton </div><div class="t m1a6 xca h61 y8ee ff2 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Send your dollars off for this quarter&apos;s Thirteenth </div><div class="t m15c xca h61 y8ef ff2 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath projects on the back cover. </div><div class="t m700 x93 h26 y8f0 ff5 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Twenty</div><div class="t m6f7 x5d h18 y3b1 ff5 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m701 x32 h26 y3b1 ff5 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">five </div><div class="t m702 xb9 h26 y8f1 ff5 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">percent of the offering will support these projects. </div><div class="t m62c xbc h2d y8f2 ff2 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">75 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
